description: About 3,500 people went to Vale Earth Fair on Guernsey, which has had no Covid-19 cases since May.
title: Vale Earth Fair festival held in Covid-free Guernsey

maintext: "It was unfortunate we had to turn some people away at the door towards the end of the day, but we can only let so many people on the site.
